data.oai_dc:dc: Aphrocallistes vastus single nucleotide polymorphism (SNP) genotypes for samples used in population analyses (all samples from sample sites with n > 5) excluding sequencing controls. Samples are identified by sequencing barcode with sample site identifiers in the second column. Data are organized into two columns per locus with GenAlEx format (A=1,C=2,G=3,T=4, missing=0).
